  "instructions": [
    "Heat butter in a large Dutch oven over medium-high heat.",
    "Sear lamb shoulder until browned on all sides, then set aside.",
    "Reduce heat to medium and sauté onion, carrot, and celery until tender.",
    "Add garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add flour and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Return lamb to pot and add salt and black pepper.",
    "Pour in 1 cup of water and bring to a boil.",
    "Transfer pot to oven and braise lamb for 2 hours.",
    "Stir in grana padano and lemon juice.",
    "Serve lamb with parsley on top and a side of sautéed vegetables."
